\item $Q$ the finite set of states of the head and  $q_0\in Q$ is the initial state;
\item $\delta : Q\times\Gamma^k\to Q\times\Gamma^k\times\{\leftarrow,\cdot\,
,\rightarrow\}^k$ the transition function. Given the state of the head and the letter associated, it reads on the tape, depending on its position, the head can change state, replace the letter and move by one cell at most.
\item $Q_F\subset Q$ the set of final states, when a final state is
reached, the computation stops and the output is the value currently written on the tape. 
\end{itemize}

